OverHistory.NewCommentry: Trent Boult to Ayush Badoni Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Trent Boult bowling to Ayush Badoni, good length ball, pitching on off stump, Ayush Badoni plays an aggressive on drive on the front foot WICKET Ayush Badoni lbw Trent Boult (Lucknow Super Giants 15 Runs for 2 wickets)
OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Two in two for Boult and the Royals! WICKET Ayush Badoni lbw Trent Boult (Lucknow Super Giants 15 Runs for 2 wickets). Trent Boult bowling to Ayush Badoni, good length ball, pitching on off stump, swings back into the batter and crashes Ayush Badoni on his pads, the umpire raises his finger for the LBW and Ayush has a chat with his skipper and decides to review this, Ball Tracking shows THREE REDS and he has to depart.
